{
  "chapter": 1,
  "chapter_summary": "一个荒废的死镇，一位装瞎的盲者柳明秋潜入侦查。铁大爷率五十一骑来到此镇，身边带着一顶神秘轿子，轿中却是个穿翠绿长衫的诡异老人。柳明秋脱身后，在荒废宅院中与江南慕容公子会面，告知铁大爷此行带了二十七名精锐杀手，其中最可怕的是曾赴东瀛伊贺谷受训的暗杀组织'丝'。慕容世家传人品鉴力极高，二人谈笑间透露出对局势的从容。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "叙述者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "——那些让人愉快的声音到哪里去了?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "叙述者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "——那些店铺里的伙计正和妇女老媪讨价还价的声音，刀勺子在锅子里翻炒烹炸的声音，妈妈打小孩屁股的声音，小孩的哭声，小姑娘吃吃的笑声，骰子掷在碗里的声音，醉汉的笑声，酒楼上那些假冒江南歌语唱小调的声音。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "叙述者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "——狗就是狗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "叙述者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "——归人的归心似箭，只恨不得能早一点回到父母妻子儿女的温情里，过客赶路心急，怎么会如此从容?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "叙述者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "——铁大爷没有别的名字，他就姓铁，他的名字就叫铁大爷。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "叙述者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "——铁大爷身高七尺九寸半，体重一百三十九斤，据说他最宠爱的女人羊玉曾经要求他为她做一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "羊玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真的有三百八十七条，一条都不少，每一条都硬得像铁一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "叙述者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "——在某些方面来说，外门硬功无敌的男子汉，是绝对比不上一个温温柔柔的小男人的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "叙述者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "——那些有眼无珠的王八蛋，怎么会认得出你这个瞎子，就是柳先生?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_san_shen",
      "speaker_name": "三婶",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "三婶，你好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_san_shen",
      "speaker_name": "三婶",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "我好、我好，你也好、你也好。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_san_shen",
      "speaker_name": "三婶",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "我们大家都好，还都活着，怎么会不好?",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_san_shen",
      "text": "侄少爷呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_san_shen",
      "speaker_name": "三婶",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "他也不错，他也很好，",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_san_shen",
      "speaker_name": "三婶",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "看样子他最近也死不了的。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_san_shen",
      "text": "那就好极了，",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_san_shen",
      "text": "我能不能进去看看他?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_san_shen",
      "speaker_name": "三婶",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "能，能，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_san_shen",
      "speaker_name": "三婶",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "你进去，他本来就在等你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "十叔，你去过了?有没有看见那个大块头?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "那个大块头有没有看见你?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "铁大爷又不是瞎子，怎么会看不见我?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "可是，就算他看见你，一定也好像没看见一样，因为他根本看不出你是谁。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "对不对?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "你不能怪他们，我装瞎子的本事，一向是第一流的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "就算你装得不像，他们也想不到的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "天下第一眼，“明察秋毫\"柳明秋柳先生，怎么会是个瞎子，谁想得到?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "那个大块头是不是还和以前一样?身边总是带着一大票中看不中吃的小伙子?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "这一次好像有一点不同。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "这一次他带去的人，至少有二十七个有用的，而且非常有用。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "非常有用?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "多么有用?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "公子虽然是江南人，想必也应该知道，在湖广闽粤的名公巨卿府邸中，有一个最出名的戏班子，叫做弄玉班。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "我早就听说过了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "其实他们真正精通的，并不是这些事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "不是这些事是什么事?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "是杀人。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "要怎么样才能在最适当的时候，把握着最有利的机会，用最快速有效的方法杀人，而且要在杀人后全身而退。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "这才是弄玉班那些漂亮的男优们，受训的最终目的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "难道那些可爱的小男孩都是可怕的杀手?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "杀人的代价是不是通常都要比取悦别人的代价高得多?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "是的，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "一般说来，通常都是这样子的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "所以他们明为优娼，其实却从小就要接受非常严格残酷的杀人训练。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "经过十年到十二年这种训练后，他们每个人都被训练成一个非常有效的杀人者。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "有没有人不能接受呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "不能接受，就要被淘汰。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "被淘汰的，就只有死?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "经过每年一次的淘汰之后，剩下来的人已经不多了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "这些人每一个都冷酷无情，都有毒蛇般的灵动狡黠，狐一般的奸猾，骆驼般的忍耐，而且都精于缩骨、易容、狙击、突击、刺杀，尤其是其中一部分叫'丝'的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "丝?",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "丝缎的丝?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "他们为什么要叫做丝?",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "因为他们都是经过特别挑选，在弄玉班的训练之后，又被送到东瀛扶桑的'伊贺谷'去受三年忍术训练的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "经过这种更严格更残酷的忍者训练之后，他们每个人都能将身体像蛇一样扭曲变形，躲藏在一个别人绝不能躲进去的隐秘藏身处，等到一个最有利的时机，才风窜而出，狙击突袭，杀人于瞬息之间。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容公子",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "哦!",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "他们有时甚至可以不饮不食、不眠不动，蜷曲在一个很窄小的地方三两天，可是只要一动，对方通常就死定了。",
      "tone": "认真",
